    "synopsis": "Sarevok is both Orin's grandfather and father. Orin's mother was his favourite, and he wanted her to become the next Chosen. Ordering her to sacrifice Orin to Bhaal. Orin defended herself and instead killed her own mother and in turn became the Chosen.Sarevok has presevered Orin's mothers body in a secret chamber in the Bhaal Temple, where players can discover it.",
    "how_to_trigger": "1) Goto 95.957; -60.46; 1018.412) Open debug book CTRL+SHFT+93) Choose option 7: Useful Spells4) Choose Speak with Dead.5) Use speak with dead spell on body."
